This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with improving the quality of Neural Machine Translation systems. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as these fields are closely related to NMT. Additionally, the paper mentions being inspired by work in computer vision, so it could also be relevant to cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
